Syrian-Caramanian Line. Port Said, Jaffa, Beyrout,
                        Tripoli, Alexandretta, Mersina, Febr. 18;
                            March 4, 18 ; April 1. 15, 29 ; May 13, 27 ;
                            June 10, 24.

A general strike has been proclaimed as a protest against the arrests ;
                            32,000 workmen are idle. Several tramway employes have been injured.
